from an university, she’s been developing backbone systems of local governments and companies in the IT industry.</p>\n<p>Currently she is not only working as an engineer, but also producing watercolors as an artist. She produces her art by the beautiful scene that comes to her mind.  </p>\n<p><strong>The way to get Yoko’s art</strong><br>\nIf you tell me what you want, I create it.<br>\nPlease decide the price on your own after obtaining the art.<br>\nIf that’s what you want to do, you don’t need to send me anything back.  </p>\n<p><strong>Contact</strong><br>\nPlease feel free to contact me if you are interested in my art.  </p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://forms.gle/HMVYyZf8vrsakRoC6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Contact Form</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yokotamanoko/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Instagram</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/yokotamanoko\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/yokotamanoko\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Weibo</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"About me","date":null,"description":null,"socialImage":"/media/aboutme.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/pages/about/"}}}